 ### Featured Trees

 #### Oak Tree

 **Scientific Name**:Quercus robur

 Known for its streangth and longevity, the oak is a symbol of emdurance.

 ![](https://treenewal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/oak-tree-care.png)

 ---

 #### Pine Tree

 **Scientific Named**: Pinus

 Evergreen and aromatic, pine trees thrive in colder regions.

 ![](https://www.shutterstock.com/image-photo/snow-covered-pine-trees-winter-260nw-2635668635.jpg)

